    <item>
      <title>摩根大通总裁米歇尔：美联储降息“没什么好争论的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-rate-cut-nothing-to-quibble-about-jpm-s-michele-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司全球固定收益主管鲍勃·米歇尔 (Bob Michele) 在彭博电视上表示，美联储降息和预测“比我们想象的要温和一些”。联邦公开市场委员会以 11 比 1 的投票结果将联邦基金利率下调至 4.75% 至 5% 的区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-rate-cut-nothing-to-quibble-about-jpm-s-michele-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:32:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储四年来首次降息，信贷风险指标有所下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/credit-risk-gauge-eases-as-fed-cuts-for-first-time-in-4-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦公开市场委员会 (FOMC) 为实现美国经济罕见的软着陆而降息之后，衡量美国公司债券市场风险的一项关键指标周三出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/credit-risk-gauge-eases-as-fed-cuts-for-first-time-in-4-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街对美联储四年来首次降息“鸽派”反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/wall-street-reacts-to-dovish-first-fed-rate-cut-in-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国央行四年来首次降息半个百分点后，交易员增加了对美联储进一步放松政策的押注，美国股市创下历史新高，美元小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/wall-street-reacts-to-dovish-first-fed-rate-cut-in-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场参与者称美联储降息对信贷有利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-is-a-positive-for-credit-market-participants-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三宣布四年多来首次降息，将利率下调半个百分点，信贷衍生品利差随之收窄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-is-a-positive-for-credit-market-participants-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:24:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储选择降息半个百分点，交易员押注进一步宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储官员将基准利率下调半个基点、导致短期国债收益率下降后，交易员们加大了对美联储未来宽松步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储历史性决定下调基准利率半个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-cuts-benchmark-rate-by-a-half-point-in-historic-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储已下调利率。联邦公开市场委员会以 11 比 1 的投票结果将联邦基金利率下调至 4.75% 至 5% 的区间，此前一年多来，该利率一直维持在 20 年来的最高水平。这并非一致决定。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-cuts-benchmark-rate-by-a-half-point-in-historic-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储自 2020 年以来首次降息后，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三将基准利率下调半个百分点，金价因此升至历史新高，此举标志着美联储开始积极转变政策以刺激劳动力市场并保护经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
